elements._description:
Welcome to JORM! this is supposed to be a tutorial area.
Here are some important commands:

look -> view current room

look TARGET -> look at a target

get / drop ITEM -> get or drop an item

stats -> view your stats

equip -> view equipment

equip ITEM -> equip item

use SKILL on TARGET -> use a skill on a target

use ITEM on TARGET -> use item on a target

level -> levels you up, remember to specify
which stat to allocated points to like this
"level grit"

practice -> view all skills you can learn
practice SKILL xxx -> practice a skill by xxx amount, example:
"practice swing 20"

skill -> view current skills you know 
skill SKILL_NAME -> get extra info about a specific skill

affects -> view your afflictions

go LOCATION -> go through a room exit

lastly there is 
help -> view all commands in game

thats all!

Again, welcome to JORM! This is the start of your adventure.
To the north is Pernion.
To the east is Ellenia.
To the south is Henesys.
And to the west is Kerning City.

You find yourself in the dimly lit streets of Kerning City.
A sprawling urban jungle. Neon signs flicker and hum.
Shadows dance along the graffiti covered walls of grimy brick buildings.
You find yourself at the base of the mountain, in the city of Perion. Where warriors come to climb the mountain to train and hone their skills.
You find yourself in the nice city of Henesys with a pleasant view of the the plains accompanied with a nice breeze.
You find yourself in the dense forest of Ellenia, a secluded city where the forest hums with life and magic.
The back streets of Kerning city where anything can happen. But what is that smell... the sewers?
The back streets of Kerning city where anything can happen

The night sky stretches endlessly above, you can see the city in the distance.
In the vertical distance...

Wooden beams are used to close the gaping holes between the floors.
